      "title": "Calculate the total mass",
      "content": "To find the mean mass, sum all the individual masses. Adding 4,020 + 4,020 + 3,040 + 4,060 + 3,160 step-by-step: <ul><li>4,020 + 4,020 = 8,040</li><li>8,040 + 3,040 = 11,080</li><li>11,080 + 4,060 = 15,140</li><li>15,140 + 3,160 = 18,300</li></ul> Total mass = 18,300 grams."
